Package io.openems.edge.common.modbusslave

Class ModbusRecordCycleValue<T extends OpenemsComponent>

java.lang.Object
io.openems.edge.common.modbusslave.ModbusRecord
io.openems.edge.common.modbusslave.ModbusRecordCycleValue<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the OpenemsComponent
public class ModbusRecordCycleValue<T extends OpenemsComponent> extends ModbusRecord
ModbusRecordCycleValues allow to receive a ModbusRecord via a Function. The Function is executed in the 'run()' method of the Modbus-TCP-Api-Controller.

      public void updateValue(T component)
      Update the Value of this ModbusRecord.

      This method is called on every cycle by the run()-method of the Modbus-TCP-Api-Controller. Value is set to 'null' if provided 'component' is null.

      Parameters:
